---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-[#94a3b8]">
      <p><strong class="text-[#e2e8f0]">Last updated:</strong> May 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as when you contact us. We also automatically collect certain information about your device, including your IP address, browser type, and operating system.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to operate and maintain our website, respond to your comments and questions, and improve our content and user experience.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings. See our <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a> for more details.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party services such as analytics and advertising partners. These services may collect information about your online activities over time.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">5. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">6. Children\'s Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our website is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#e2e8f0] mt-8">8. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
